data.description: Are you looking for beautiful mountain views in the City of Denver?  Look no further!  This ranch style house, located in Villa Park is a wonderful opportunity.  As one of the last affordable areas in the city proper, this West Denver neighborhood is a quick commute to Downtown, the Highlands, and Sloan's Lake.  Close to 6th Ave., it is one of the easiest areas of town to get to the mountains!  4 bedrooms makes it a great opportunity for families, roommates, or for folks who just like a little extra space.  Do not let this opportunity pass you by!
